rows.name:
Friends read book called
How Wars Profit Nopon?

rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Is about analyzing potential profits for
Nopon trade guilds if war break out
between Superbia and Invidia.

rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Book written by Superbian, and
full of ridiculous misconception
about Nopon culture!

rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Pretty scary to thinking people believe
this nonsense. But also very funny to
read, so everyone here enjoy book lots.

rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0005
rows.name:
When feeling down, Smismi just
break out book and laugh so hard,
forget any bad thing happen!

rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0006
rows.name:
If friends interested, should try
purchase book at Haskefell Books
in Superbia!
